root: ^Stop resting, it's time to get down to business!
^We have been entrusted with a responsible task, we need to get to the village before the goblins and protect the inhabitants.
^Goblins are the weakest monsters, even villagers can fight them off on their own.
^The village is under the protection of our guild.
^If a request has been received, then we must come to the rescue.
^You haven’t fought for a long time, it’s time to remember what your father taught you, otherwise you won’t be of any use.
